  <h1>Welcome!</h1>

  <p>Thanks for taking our test. Now that you have your environment up and running, you're ready to begin.</p>

  <p>For this exercise, we have a small database of customers, with a firstName, lastName, and dueMonthly fields, which represents the amount of money they pay us each month."</p>

